  <brief_title>Development of Bone Grafts Using Adipose Derived Stem Cells and Different Scaffolds</brief_title>
  <official_title>Development of Bone Grafts Using Adipose Derived Stem Cells and Different Scaffolds: Impact of Pre-engineered Capillaries in Critical Size Grafts</official_title>
